Gemini Dragon laughs from both heads as it looked down at the 
immobile Trainwreck(he has to be immobile if his wheels are smashed 
in.

Gemini: "We are just getting warmed up... Literally! Amphorbasis!"

With that one word each head began to crackle with energy as the tail 
did as well. A second later each head sent out an energizen beam of 
fire and liquid Nitrogen before the tail sent out a blast of 
electricity. Each blast then combined and swirled in the air before a 
singular massive blast flew straight down at Trainwreck. Nearby Zero 
Reaches methos and glares as he grabs his shoulder and spins him 
around to meet his glare.

Zero: "So we meet again... perhaps we are destined to clash... Let's 
finish this!"

With those words Zero slams his Energy blade into the blade of 
Methos's energy scythe each bot pushing into their weapons to through 
the other one off balanca.
